The paper discusses a caching architecture for storage systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The caching is done at the Operating System (OS) level, which suggests the paper could also belong to the Operating Systems (cs.OS) category. The paper also discusses workload characterization and optimization, which could fall under the categories of Architecture (cs.AR), Databases (cs.DB), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
